                <note rend="inline" type="source">Paris Peace Conf. 184.82/2: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Commission to Negotiate Peace</gloss>
                        to the <gloss type="to">Acting Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">[<placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Paris</hi>
                        </placeName>,] <date calendar="gregorian" when="1918-12-23">December 23,
                            1918</date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>76. [From <persName corresp="#p_LR1">Lansing</persName>.] Your 67 December 20th
                    2:00 p.m. The matter dealt with by the Associated Press under date of December
                    18th mentioned in your telegram has not been discussed here. <persName
                        corresp="#p_LR1">Lansing</persName>.</p>
                <closer>
                    <hi rend="smallcaps">Am</hi> [<hi rend="smallcaps">erican</hi>] <hi
                        rend="smallcaps">Mission</hi>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
